            "_key": "span-1760818344456-2fb77kehi",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "2. 食生活と栄養管理"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "h3"
      },
      {
        "_key": "block-1760818344456-aqxsw5r29",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818344456-qhg10bwe5-175ae62b-7ba4-4cd8-af9a-9a3e8b71e891",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "夜勤中の食事のポイント"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "block-1760818344456-50ey2zyyy",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818344456-xac24ovv9",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "夜勤中の食事は、エネルギー補給だけでなく、眠気防止や消化への負担軽減も考慮する必要があります。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "block-1760818344456-xnivy0z1l",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818344456-v4wqu7olp-255577a5-9eb9-48b0-9ee8-51b8e3a6d229",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "*   "
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818344456-v4wqu7olp-9ce8c92b-212f-4a6f-b097-0842cca5538f",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "食事のタイミング:"
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818344456-v4wqu7olp-85e032b4-6ae1-4d2b-8cf7-b4caf117df5d",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": " 勤務時間に合わせて、規則正しい時間に食事を摂るように心がけましょう。特に、深夜帯の食事は少量にし、消化の良いものを選ぶようにしましょう。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "block-1760818344456-6ppwcn4u8",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818344456-l4bu9u1ws-8a54d9be-26c5-417e-9854-dfb9bf70dced",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "*   "
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818344456-l4bu9u1ws-f2469980-82af-4b54-b858-89e069d748a1",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "おすすめの食材:"
