            "marks": [],
            "text": "*   "
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818344456-203ic4zop-1917d081-cc14-42d3-862c-c78ba0e224a8",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ],
            "text": "マッサージやストレッチ:"
          },
          {
            "_key": "span-1760818344456-203ic4zop-5b1ddd63-6c03-4d39-a1c6-4a4e13edf1ad",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": " 身体の緊張をほぐすことで、心身のリラックスに繋がります。"
