            "_key": "span-1760818344456-5vkc3z4f7-c6628893-06a4-450a-a1e4-eec30280befc",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": " 一人で抱え込まず、遠慮なく同僚や上司に助けを求めるようにしましょう。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "internal-link-28d08a05-b892-452c-920d-bb0b2d24bffb",
