        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "span-373389077394698207",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "まとめ"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "h2"
      },
      {
        "_key": "summary-53a5abe8-34ed-4c4f-b10c-20b01fe09cbf",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "summary-span-bfbb74a1-41e2-49d0-b9f6-ac5e6587409d",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "夜勤がつらいときの乗り越え方でお伝えした内容を振り返ると、日々の現場で大切にしたいポイントが幾つか見えてきます。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "summary-da8b9be7-5f0c-412a-9e5f-25e34ecfd583",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "summary-span-403dce6f-5fcc-4cf7-8430-a68a87c33493",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "すぐに試しやすい行動のヒントは次の通りです。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "summary-bullet-3a2882e6-ed29-4f96-ab71-75fe9b62d47e",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "summary-bullet-span-ce828ee1-d104-4417-a556-f615f02f4305",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "生活リズムの乱れ：昼夜逆転の生活は、睡眠不足や食生活の偏りを引き起こしやすくなります。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "summary-bullet-707bf784-e5d2-4436-8194-4d1941ef5ae0",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "summary-bullet-span-e10b0a59-59ae-45bb-a78c-0e36066a9edc",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "体力的な負担：長時間勤務や不規則な休憩時間、患者さんの介助などで、体が疲弊しやすくなります。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "summary-bullet-c9a5825d-8793-4bd1-a582-125fd90fe49e",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "summary-bullet-span-c875ff56-2750-4550-b31e-f40199cb38c4",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "精神的な負担：夜間の緊急対応や、日中よりも少ない人数での業務は、精神的なプレッシャーとなることがあります。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
      },
      {
        "_key": "summary-18ff1cee-dd01-436f-99b1-fe74a4e3fa20",
        "_type": "block",
        "children": [
          {
            "_key": "summary-span-a0fd7a10-38d9-4088-b160-57c75ce8de2e",
            "_type": "span",
            "marks": [],
            "text": "あわてず一歩ずつ、チームと情報を共有しながら進めれば大丈夫です。今日の学びを小さく実践し、次の勤務につなげていきましょう。"
          }
        ],
        "markDefs": [],
        "style": "normal"
